            "type": "section", 
            "text": "<p>Ifrits are humans whose ancestry includes beings of elemental fire, such as efreet. Ifrits have pointed ears, red or mottled horns on the brow, and hair that flickers and waves as if it were aflame.</p>"
        }, 
        {
            "source": "Bestiary 2", 
